body: My name is Dharen Paulino. I am a senior student at Burton High school, who is taking big steps to the next level. I am a student athlete that plays basketball for the school for the past 4 years and I play with different type of basketball club.The clubs I play for are Sf Flight and Dc Knights and I really enjoy playing with them. I am planning to go to college and my choices are sf state and university of Santa Clara and major on pharmacist or become a physical therapy. I also plan to play basketball along my way to college and be part of a college team.
